This folder contains CFD data for the test cases used in the paper 
“Sparse-Supervised Hybrid Parameterized Physics-Informed Neural Networks for Incompressible Flows Across Reynolds Numbers.”
The data were generated using OpenFOAM-12 and validated against reference data from the literature by Armaly et al. (1983).
Each CSV file is named according to the corresponding Reynolds number (for example, BFSDataRe100.csv corresponds to Re = 100).
Every file contains five columns: x, y, u, v, and p.
For the pure PINN approach, the entire dataset is used for validation.
